T*
(- Misunderstanding the core focus of Probability: sample spaces, favorable outcomes, and) Tj
T*
(probability rules.) Tj
T*
(- Counting outcomes incorrectly or forgetting total outcomes.) Tj
T*
(- Jumping to an answer without showing the steps or reasoning clearly.) Tj
T*
(- Practising Probability without checking whether the method matches the question being) Tj
T*
(asked.) Tj
